===============================================================================
Compilation: (base directory: A2)
Steps:
    1. $ premake4 gmake
    2. $ make
    3. $ ./A2

Machine: gl13
===============================================================================
Manual:

All required features implemented.

The default values:
near plane: 5.0f;
far plane: 15.0f;
fov: 30.0f;
eye pos = (5.0f, 2.0f, 10.0f);

I used 6 different color for gnomons.

Model Frame:
framecolorbase_x1 = glm::vec3(0.0f, 1.0f, 0.0f);
framecolorbase_y1 = glm::vec3(1.0f, 0.0f, 0.0f);
framecolorbase_z1 = glm::vec3(0.0f, 0.0f, 1.0f);

World Frame:
framecolorbase_x2 = glm::vec3(0.0f, 1.0f, 1.0f);
framecolorbase_y2 = glm::vec3(1.0f, 1.0f, 0.0f);
framecolorbase_z2 = glm::vec3(1.0f, 0.0f, 1.0f);